messages.content:
This is a missed-optimization in InstCombine.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i8 @rem_euclid_non_const_pow2_commuted(i8 %0, i8 %1) {
  %pow2 = shl i8 1, %0
  %rem = srem i8 %1, %pow2
  %cond = icmp slt i8 %rem, 0
  %add = add i8 %pow2, %rem
  %sel = select i1 %cond, i8 %add, i8 %rem
  ret i8 %sel
}

```

However, current LLVM cannot optimize the source program. The expected optimized program is
```llvm
define i8 @rem_euclid_non_const_pow2_commuted(i8 %0, i8 %1) {
  %notmask = shl nsw i8 -1, %0
  %3 = xor i8 %notmask, -1
  %sel = and i8 %1, %3
  ret i8 %sel
}

```
